      "text": "Politics vs Technology"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Politics vs Technology"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "2 Jan 94"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "From: Mike Ingle > But"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "could the government ban a"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "book today? Of course not,"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "at least not"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "after one person typed it"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "or scanned it into a"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "computer. Technological\ngains are permanent. The"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "political approach is only useful"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "as a\ntactical weapon, to hold"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "them off until technological solutions"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "are\nin place. If you want"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "to change the world, don't"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "protest. Write code!"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "This position seems to be"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "fast becoming cypherpunks dogma, but"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "I don't\nagree.  The notion"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "that we can just fade"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "into cypherspace and ignore\nthe unpleasant"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "political realities is unrealistic, in"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "my view."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Have people forgotten the Clipper"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "proposal, with the possible follow-on"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "to\nmake non-Clipper encryption illegal? "
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "To the extent this proposal"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "has been\nor will be defeated,"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "it will happen through political"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "maneuvering, not\ntechnology."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Have people forgotten the PGP"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "export investigation?  Phil Zimmermann"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "hasn't.\nHe and others may be"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "facing the prospect of ten"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "years in prison if they"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "were\nfound guilty of illegal export."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": " If anyone has any"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "suggestions for how to\nescape from"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "jail into cyberspace I'd like"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "to hear about them."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Mike's SecureDrive is a terrific"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "program for protecting privacy. "
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "But\nif we want to keep"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "keys secret from politically-motivated investigations,\nwe"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "have to rely on the"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "very political and non-technological Fifth"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Amendment\n(an amendment which Mike Godwin"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "of EFF and others contend"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "does not actually\nprotect disclosure of"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "cryptographic keys).  Again, we"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "need to win political,\nnot technological,"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "victories in order to protect"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "our privacy."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "I even question Mike's point"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "about the government's inability to"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "ban books.\nLook at the difficulty"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "in keeping PGP available in"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "this country even though\nit is"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "legal.  Not only have"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "FTP sites been steadily closed"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "down, even the\nkey servers have"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "as well.  And this"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "is legal software.  "
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Sure, this software is currently"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "available overseas, but that is"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "because\nPGP's only legal limitations are"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "the U.S. patent issues. "
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Imagine how much\nworse it would"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "be if non-escrowed encryption were"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "made illegal in a broad\nrange"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "of countries, with stringent limits"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "on net access to countries"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "which\npromote illegal software?  Here"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "again, these kinds of decisions"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "will be made\nin the political"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "realm."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Fundamentally, I believe we will"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "have the kind of society"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "that most people\nwant.  If"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "we want freedom and privacy,"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "we must persuade others that"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "these\nare worth having.  There"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "are no shortcuts.  Withdrawing"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "into technology\nis like pulling the"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "blankets over your head. "
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "It feels good for a"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "while, until\nreality catches up. "
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The next Clipper or Digital"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Telephony proposal will\nprovide a rude"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "awakening."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Hal Finney  \nhal@rain.org "
